elemines 0.3
------------

Requires EFL 1.8
- Sound support using multisense


elemines 0.2.3
--------------

Mines count and board size are now defined in the edje theme
Big code refactoring/improvement by Cedric Bail:
- most of the layout done with edje
- use eina iterators to walk the matrix
- use ecore getopt
- add support for QuickLaunch

New theme:
- default-big (20x10, 24 mines)

New translation:
- polish


elemines 0.2.2
--------------

Fix the middle click feature once again
Fix flags accounting
Validate user data to prevent endless loop

New translation:
- russian


elemines 0.2.1
--------------

Fix the middle click feature
Detect high score

New translations:
- esperanto
- galician
- italiano
- korean
- portuguese


elemines 0.2
------------

Config to change mine number in game
Add score management using etrophy
Implement third click
Resize the red flags and other cosmetic changes
Translation support (french)


